Package univie.cs.psps.utils

Interface Summary
AggregationProtocol An interface for aggregation protocols to be observed by AggregationProtocolObserver.
 

Class Summary
AggregationProtocolObserver Observes an AggregationProtocol during the simulation, prints the results to the standard output or to a file for plotting, and determines when to stop the simulation.
FormattedStatistics A subclass of SummaryStatistics for convenient printing of a table of statistics.
GraphWriter A subclass of GraphObserver to save the network graph to a .dot file, intended for plotting with Graphviz.
ProtocolUtils A utility class for commonly used functions in protocols.
RandUndirectionalNI A NodeInitializer creating a given number of random undirectional links for each node.
WireClusters Creates a network topology of several clusters of nodes, which are fully connected within the cluster, but any two clusters are only connected over a single edge.
